question.title: android proguard makes the youtube api oauth disabled?

node.contents: Are you sure ``proguard.config`` is assigned two values or only the latter one? I would guess that you have to combine it to one statement only by adding ``:proguard-flurry.txt`` at the end of first setter.

node.contents: I got it, add -keep class com.google.api.services.** { *; } in proguard-google-api-client.txt. It'll work.
